overview: The user initiated a request to enhance the aesthetic appeal of their
  sleep questionnaire application, which they felt was functional but visually
  uninspired. The agent conducted a detailed analysis of the existing design,
  pinpointing areas like the generic color palette, bland backgrounds, and
  uninviting form elements. The approach taken was to transform the app's visual
  language into a calming, professional, and sleep-themed experience. This
  involved updating the global color palette, redesigning the main
  QuestionnaireForm layout, enriching the IntroSection with more engaging
  elements, and refining the styling of core UI components like CheckboxField,
  Checkbox, and Slider. The DaytimeSection was also updated to demonstrate
  improved visual grouping and typography. The outcome is a significantly more
  polished and user-friendly interface that better reflects the app's purpose.
